<h1>Stepbar or multi-step process</h1>

<h2>Introduction</h2>
<p>In this example we will see how to improve the vocalization of a “stepbar” component.</p>
<p>To achieve this we will use the <a href="https://boosted.orange.com/docs/5.1/components/stepped-process/">stepbar</a> component available in the <a href="http://boosted.orange.com/">Boosted</a> library. Some styles have been modified to fit onto a single line.</p>

